# 2p_summary — focused test for the summary-screen "Next round in
# Ns" countdown. Both players sit still through round 1 → summary →
# round 2. Screenshots taken DURING the summary phase from both
# sides. The displayed countdown should tick down on both sides
# and show within ~0.5 s of each other (host broadcasts at start of
# summary; client decays its local copy).

window 1280 720
out build/shots/net/sum_host
network host 24071
name HostA

# Round 1 starts ~tick 130, ends on time_limit at ~tick 610.
# Summary runs ~610 → ~850 (4 s in shot mode).
# Burst-screenshot the summary phase so we can read the countdown.
at 650 shot summary_t650
at 700 shot summary_t700
at 770 shot summary_t770
at 830 shot summary_t830
at 870 shot lobby_after
at 950 end
